---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/PageHero.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="技術紹介 | Esperance">
  <PageHero eyebrow="CORE TECHNOLOGY" title="技術紹介" />

  <!-- Intro copy block -->
  <section class="bg-[#050505]">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-[24px] max-[640px]:px-[16px]">
      <div class="mx-auto mt-[70px] w-[800px] text-center max-[960px]:w-full">
        <h2
          class="font-[Noto_Serif_JP] text-[24px] font-bold leading-[38.4px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#F0F0F0]
                 max-[640px]:text-[20px] max-[640px]:leading-[32px]"
        >
          失われた設計図を、<br />
          最新技術で「再定義」する。
        </h2>

        <div
          class="mx-auto mt-[20px] w-[480px] border-t-2 border-[#D32F2F]
                 max-[640px]:w-[240px]"
        ></div>

        <p
          class="mt-[22px] font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[16px] font-[350] leading-[28.8px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#E0E0E0]
                 max-[640px]:text-[14px] max-[640px]:leading-[26px]"
        >
          私たちの強みは、単なる金型製造ではありません。<br />
          リバースエンジニアリングによる「復元」、流動解析による「最適化」、<br />
          そして熟練の職人による「仕上げ」。<br />
          アナログとデジタルの融合が、KATANAの魂を現代に蘇らせます。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tech blocks -->
  <section class="bg-[#050505]">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-[24px] pb-[120px] pt-[80px]">
      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-[1200px] flex-col gap-[90px]">

        <!-- 1段目：画像 → テキスト -->
        <div
          class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-[1200px] items-center gap-[98px] px-[20px]
                 max-[960px]:flex-col max-[960px]:items-stretch max-[960px]:gap-[28px] max-[960px]:px-0"
        >
          <!-- 画像枠（580×363） -->
          <div
            class="relative h-[363px] w-[580px]
                   max-[960px]:w-full max-[960px]:h-[320px]
                   max-[640px]:h-[220px]"
          >
            <div class="pointer-events-none absolute right-[12px] top-[12px] h-[22px] w-[22px] border-r-2 border-t-2 border-[#D32F2F]"></div>

            <img
              src="/images/technology/img1-tech.png"
              alt="Reverse Engineering"
              class="h-full w-full object-cover"
            />

            <div class="pointer-events-none absolute bottom-[12px] left-[12px] h-[22px] w-[22px] border-b-2 border-l-2 border-[#D32F2F]"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- テキスト枠（522×358） -->
          <div
            class="flex h-[358px] w-[522px] flex-col gap-[9px]
                   max-[960px]:w-full max-[960px]:h-auto"
          >
            <p class="font-[Oswald] text-[14px] font-normal leading-[25.92px] tracking-[1.4px] text-[#D32F2F] uppercase">
              REVERSE ENGINEERING
            </p>

            <h3 class="font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[32px] font-bold leading-[41.6px] tracking-[0.8px] text-white">
              リバースエンジニアリング
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-[10px] font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[16px] font-[350] leading-[28.8px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#E0E0E0]">
              純正パーツが現存していても、当時の設計図が残っているとは限りません。
              私たちは最新の3Dスキャナを駆使し、実物をミクロン単位でデータ化。
              経年劣化による歪みや摩耗を補正し、「新品当時の本来あるべき形状」をデジタル上で復元します。
            </p>

            <div class="mt-[18px] w-full border-t border-[#333333]">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-[#333333] py-[15px]">
                <p class="font-[Oswald] text-[14.4px] font-bold leading-[25.92px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#D32F2F]">
                  EQUIPMENT
                </p>
                <p class="font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[14.4px] font-[350] leading-[25.92px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#F0F0F0]">
                  KEYENCE VL-700
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-[#333333] py-[15px]">
                <p class="font-[Oswald] text-[14.4px] font-bold leading-[25.92px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#D32F2F]">
                  PRECISION
                </p>
                <p class="font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[14.4px] font-[350] leading-[25.92px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#F0F0F0]">
                  ±0.01mm Scan Accuracy
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2段目：テキスト → 画像 -->
        <div
          class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-[1200px] items-center gap-[98px] px-[20px]
                 max-[960px]:flex-col max-[960px]:items-stretch max-[960px]:gap-[28px] max-[960px]:px-0"
        >
          <!-- テキスト枠 -->
          <div
            class="flex h-[358px] w-[522px] flex-col gap-[9px]
                   max-[960px]:w-full max-[960px]:h-auto max-[960px]:order-2"
          >
            <p class="font-[Oswald] text-[14px] font-normal leading-[25.92px] tracking-[1.4px] text-[#D32F2F] uppercase">
              MOLD DESIGN &amp; CAE
            </p>

            <h3 class="font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[32px] font-bold leading-[41.6px] tracking-[0.8px] text-white">
              超精密金型設計・解析
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-[10px] font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[16px] font-[350] leading-[28.8px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#E0E0E0]">
              形状を再現するだけでは不十分です。現代の樹脂素材に合わせ、金型内での樹脂の流れるスピードや温度変化を
              シミュレーション（流動解析）。「ウェルドライン（継ぎ目）」を目立たなくし、強度不足を防ぐための
              最適なゲート位置と金型構造を設計します。
            </p>

            <div class="mt-[18px] w-full border-t border-[#333333]">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-[#333333] py-[15px]">
                <p class="font-[Oswald] text-[14.4px] font-bold leading-[25.92px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#D32F2F]">
                  SOFTWARE
                </p>
                <p class="font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[14.4px] font-[350] leading-[25.92px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#F0F0F0]">
                  3D CAD / Moldflow
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-[#333333] py-[15px]">
                <p class="font-[Oswald] text-[14.4px] font-bold leading-[25.92px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#D32F2F]">
                  FEATURE
                </p>
                <p class="font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[14.4px] font-[350] leading-[25.92px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#F0F0F0]">
                  Slide Core Structure
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 画像枠 -->
          <div
            class="relative h-[363px] w-[580px]
                   max-[960px]:w-full max-[960px]:h-[320px] max-[960px]:order-1
                   max-[640px]:h-[220px]"
          >
            <div class="pointer-events-none absolute right-[12px] top-[12px] h-[22px] w-[22px] border-r-2 border-t-2 border-[#D32F2F]"></div>

            <img
              src="/images/technology/img2-tech.png"
              alt="Reverse Engineering"
              class="h-full w-full object-cover"
            />

            <div class="pointer-events-none absolute bottom-[12px] left-[12px] h-[22px] w-[22px] border-b-2 border-l-2 border-[#D32F2F]"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3段目：画像 → テキスト -->
        <div
          class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-[1200px] items-center gap-[98px] px-[20px]
                 max-[960px]:flex-col max-[960px]:items-stretch max-[960px]:gap-[28px] max-[960px]:px-0"
        >
          <!-- 画像枠（580×363） -->
          <div
            class="relative h-[363px] w-[580px]
                   max-[960px]:w-full max-[960px]:h-[320px]
                   max-[640px]:h-[220px]"
          >
            <div class="pointer-events-none absolute right-[12px] top-[12px] h-[22px] w-[22px] border-r-2 border-t-2 border-[#D32F2F]"></div>

            <img
              src="/images/technology/img3-tech.png"
              alt="Reverse Engineering"
              class="h-full w-full object-cover"
            />

            <div class="pointer-events-none absolute bottom-[12px] left-[12px] h-[22px] w-[22px] border-b-2 border-l-2 border-[#D32F2F]"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- テキスト枠（522×358） -->
          <div
            class="flex h-[358px] w-[522px] flex-col gap-[9px]
                   max-[960px]:w-full max-[960px]:h-auto"
          >
            <p class="font-[Oswald] text-[14px] font-normal leading-[25.92px] tracking-[1.4px] text-[#D32F2F] uppercase">
              PRECISION MANUFACTURING
            </p>

            <h3 class="font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[32px] font-bold leading-[41.6px] tracking-[0.8px] text-white">
              5軸加工・仕上げ
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-[10px] font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[16px] font-[350] leading-[28.8px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#E0E0E0]">
              KATANA特有の有機的な曲線を再現するために、同時5軸制御のマシニングセンタを使用。
              複雑なアンダーカット形状も、ワンチャッキングで高精度に削り出します。
              最後は職人の手による鏡面磨きで、金型の表面を極限まで滑らかに仕上げます。
            </p>

            <div class="mt-[18px] w-full border-t border-[#333333]">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-[#333333] py-[15px]">
                <p class="font-[Oswald] text-[14.4px] font-bold leading-[25.92px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#D32F2F]">
                  MACHINE
                </p>
                <p class="font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[14.4px] font-[350] leading-[25.92px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#F0F0F0]">
                  5-Axis Machining Center
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-[#333333] py-[15px]">
                <p class="font-[Oswald] text-[14.4px] font-bold leading-[25.92px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#D32F2F]">
                  FINISH
                </p>
                <p class="font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[14.4px] font-[350] leading-[25.92px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#F0F0F0]">
                  Mirror Polishing
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WORKFLOW -->
  <section class="bg-[#050505] border-t border-[#222222]">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] py-[100px]">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-[60px]">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="font-[Oswald] text-[16px] font-normal leading-[28.8px] tracking-[1.6px] text-[#D32F2F] uppercase">
            WORKFLOW
          </p>
          <h2 class="mt-[6px] font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[32px] font-bold leading-[57.6px] tracking-[0.8px] text-white">
            製作プロセス
          </h2>
        </div>

        <!-- ✅ SPだけ横スク（PC見た目は完全にそのまま） -->
        <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1000px] px-[20px] max-[640px]:px-[16px]">
          <div class="relative max-[640px]:overflow-x-auto max-[640px]:-mx-[16px] max-[640px]:px-[16px]">
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="pointer-events-none absolute left-[-15px] right-[-15px] top-[40px] h-[2px] bg-[#333333]"></div>

              <div class="relative z-10 flex items-start justify-between max-[640px]:min-w-[860px]">
                <!-- Step 01 -->
                <div class="flex w-[200px] flex-col items-center text-center">
                  <div class="relative flex h-[80px] w-[80px] items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[#333333] bg-[#111111]">
                    <span class="font-[Oswald] text-[24px] font-normal leading-[43.2px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#D32F2F]">
                      01
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="mt-[14px] font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[16px] font-bold leading-[28.8px] tracking-[0.8px] text-white">
                    3D SCAN
                  </p>
                  <p class="mt-[6px] font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[12.8px] font-[350] leading-[20.48px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#E0E0E0]">
                    実物をスキャンし<br />点群データを取得
                  </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 02 -->
                <div class="flex w-[200px] flex-col items-center text-center">
                  <div class="relative flex h-[80px] w-[80px] items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[#333333] bg-[#111111]">
                    <span class="font-[Oswald] text-[24px] font-normal leading-[43.2px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#D32F2F]">
                      02
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="mt-[14px] font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[16px] font-bold leading-[28.8px] tracking-[0.8px] text-white">
                    CAD DATA
                  </p>
                  <p class="mt-[6px] font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[12.8px] font-[350] leading-[20.48px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#E0E0E0]">
                    データを解析し<br />CADデータを作成
                  </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 03 -->
                <div class="flex w-[200px] flex-col items-center text-center">
                  <div class="relative flex h-[80px] w-[80px] items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[#333333] bg-[#111111]">
                    <span class="font-[Oswald] text-[24px] font-normal leading-[43.2px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#D32F2F]">
                      03
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="mt-[14px] font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[16px] font-bold leading-[28.8px] tracking-[0.8px] text-white">
                    MOLD
                  </p>
                  <p class="mt-[6px] font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[12.8px] font-[350] leading-[20.48px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#E0E0E0]">
                    金型を設計し<br />加工・製作
                  </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 04 -->
                <div class="flex w-[200px] flex-col items-center text-center">
                  <div class="relative flex h-[80px] w-[80px] items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[#333333] bg-[#111111]">
                    <span class="font-[Oswald] text-[24px] font-normal leading-[43.2px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#D32F2F]">
                      04
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="mt-[14px] font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[16px] font-bold leading-[28.8px] tracking-[0.8px] text-white">
                    PRODUCT
                  </p>
                  <p class="mt-[6px] font-[Noto_Sans_JP] text-[12.8px] font-[350] leading-[20.48px] tracking-[0.8px] text-[#E0E0E0]">
                    試作成形と<br />品質検査・製品化
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
